        {
            "title": "Curving the flat - Senior edition",
            "date": {
                "start": {
                    "month": 3,
                    "day": null,
                    "year": 2020
                },
                "end": {
                    "month": null,
                    "day": null,
                    "year": null
                }
            },
            "description": "Feet were gracefully moving on the grass, while hands were happily waving above everyone\u2019s head.\n\nTogether with RGB Disco we\u2019ve been organising a project during the first lockdown in 2020. As elderly people could almost not receive any visitors at that moment, and also couldn\u2019t attend all the weekly group activities, this created an opportunity for designing a social distancing event.\nTherefor I reached out to \u201cVitalis Woonzorggroep\u201d in Eindhoven, and this resulted into several social distancing disco\u2019s. We arranged an outside event and made sure all the participating people would receive their own headphones. Outside there were three dj\u2019s playing, and the people could also request songs they\u2019d like to hear.\nWith these events we wanted to bring people joy during this difficult time, while obeying the governments rules and making sure there would be no noice nuisance.",
